@davidgumberg thanks.  Interestingly the comment used to read:
`297 = ((68 * 3000) / 1000) + (31 * 3000) / 1000` however the value of `coin_selection_params_bnb.m_change_fee` has changed since I originally opened this PR (I'm not sure why atm).

In this commit: https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/commit/4fef5344288e454460b80db0316294e1ec1ad8ad the `m_change_fee` was `93`.
